heroes.name: npc_dota_hero_faceless_void
heroes.bio_loc: Darkterror the Faceless Void is a visitor from Claszureme, a realm outside of time. It remains a mystery why this being from another dimension believes the struggle for the Nemesis Stones is worth entering our physical plane, but apparently an upset in the balance of power in this world has repercussions in adjacent dimensions. Time means nothing to Darkterror, except as a way to thwart his foes and aid his allies. His long-view of the cosmos has given him a remote, disconnected quality, although in battle he is quite capable of making it personal.
heroes.hype_loc: Time is everything to Faceless Void. He speeds time to dash between locations, manipulates it to dodge attacks, stops it in a large area to devastate his foes, and given enough of it to gather resources, he can make himself unbelievably powerful.
heroes.npe_desc_loc: Can freeze his enemies in time

facets.description_loc: Faceless Void can cast Chronosphere, trapping enemies in a sphere.
facets.name: faceless_void_chronosphere

facets.description_loc: Faceless Void can cast Time Zone, dramatically slowing down enemies and speeding up allies in an area.
facets.name: faceless_void_time_zone

abilities.name: faceless_void_time_walk
abilities.desc_loc: Rushes to a target location while backtracking any damage taken the last %backtrack_duration% seconds.
abilities.lore_loc: Darkterror tears a hole in time, passing through Claszureme, and appearing back in an instant.
notes_loc: Faceless Void is invulnerable while using Time Walk.
abilities.scepter_loc: Applies a Time Lock to all units at the landing destination.
facets_loc: Prevents all damage for a short duration after casting Time Walk.

abilities.name: faceless_void_time_dilation
abilities.desc_loc: Faceless Void traps all nearby enemies in a time dilation field for %duration% seconds, extending their cooldowns and slowing their movement and attack speed by %slow%%% for each cooldown extended. Deals bonus damage per second for each cooldown. The debuff does not tick down while inside Chronosphere.
abilities.lore_loc: For those facing off against Darkterror, each moment seems to stretch into eternity.

abilities.name: faceless_void_time_lock
abilities.desc_loc: Adds the chance for an attack to lock an enemy unit in time while attacking it a second time.
abilities.lore_loc: The strike of the Faceless Void lands with dimension shifting force.

abilities.name: faceless_void_time_walk_reverse
abilities.desc_loc: Available for 1.5 seconds after landing Time Walk. If used in this period, you will reverse your time walk back to your previous cast location. Does not affect health or proc scepter hits.

abilities.name: faceless_void_distortion_field
abilities.desc_loc: Enemy Attack Projectiles within %slow_distance_max% radius are slowed by %attack_projectile_slow%%%.

talents.name: special_bonus_unique_faceless_void_4
talents.desc_loc: Grants a {s:dodge_chance_pct}% chance to avoid damage entirely. Disabled by break.

abilities.name: faceless_void_chronosphere
abilities.desc_loc: Creates a blister in spacetime, trapping all units caught in its sphere of influence and causes you to move very quickly inside it.  All ability and item cooldowns are frozen. Only Faceless Void and any units he controls are unaffected. Invisible enemies in the sphere will be revealed.
abilities.lore_loc: When a rift opens to Claszureme, all poor souls caught within will likely never return.
notes_loc: Pauses all units and buildings, friendly or enemy, except those owned by Faceless Void.
Faceless Void is never affected by Chronospheres with any owner.

abilities.name: faceless_void_time_zone
abilities.desc_loc:
Creates a blister in spacetime, altering the movement, attack, cast, projectile, and turn rate speed of all units inside. Allies have increased speed and enemies have decreased speed.

Enemies are leashed inside the Time Zone.
